[[:God]] → {{no redirect|Deity (monotheism)}} – God could not only mean the deity in monotheism but also mean the deity in polytheism. In wikipedia,the word "God" only means deity in monotheism, that is not fair. So I believe the content of this article should have a new title "Deity (monotheism)", and the title "God" should be redirected to "Deity". [[User:MacArthur1945|MacArthur1945]] ([[User talk:MacArthur1945|talk]]) 11:17, 21 October 2016 (UTC)
